column3: I-64E at 51 MM in Franklin Co:
column4: The roadway is shutdown until further notice due to a collision involving a cattle hauling trailer.

column3: I-64E at 51 MM in Franklin Co:
column4: Detour:  Exit 48/KY-151 to US-60E to US-127S, then back to I-64E.

column3: I-64E at 51 MM in Franklin Co:
column4: NOTE:  All westbound lanes will be shutdown while cattle are being offloaded.
